phrases: It looks like a princess or something to me.
What the hell was that thing?
I thought she was some kind of weird pervert.
So that shriveled-up corpse turned into a hot naked chick and attacked somebody?
Did she just plump up like instant ramen?
Lauden neiven possess terrifying regenerative powers.
No matter how much damage their bodies take,
they can absorb latena, the power humans use to live, and revive.
Their race was destroyed many years ago.
If I would only been more cautious, I would have noticed sooner.
Do not let it get to you.
The more important problem is that the monster's still out there.
We have got an emergency warrant out, but...
You doreany cannot possibly catch her.
I do not know about that.
My bullets and your sword seemed to hurt her just fine.
If she gets surrounded by a SWAT team, that will be that.
They are athletic and have great aim.
I do not train at all, so they are a lot more reliable than me.
What matters is your sense of smell in combat.
For example, why did you have a fire extinguisher when you ran down to save me?
It just felt like the right thing to do.
That is what I mean by sense of smell.
You are an unpleasant man, but in that sense, you are worthy of respect.
I am concerned about the other bolicemen.
Lauden neiven are far too dangerous.
I am getting a ride home.
That is outside the cordon we set up.
How did she get so far?
I called you here to find out.
Can she move that fast after she got an arm cut off?
I do not know is not good enough.
If we do not find her, more people are going to die.
How are you going to fix that?
That is why I was opposed to this.
No good will come of having a Semanian on the force.
Civilized society has its own set of rules, and this little girl cannot-
I think that is enough, Superintendent.
People are dying while you are standing here bitching.
If it were not for the girl, Cecil Epps would be dead,
the vampire would have gotten out without anybody noticing,
and nobody would have known a thing was wrong until morning.
If anything, we are damn lucky it worked out the way it did.
And Exedilica works for me, damn it!
You got a problem with her, you come to me first, kid!
I did not see that coming.
He is just a snot-nosed kid.
He used to piss himself all the time when he was a new recruit for the LA Police.
What, you got a problem, too?
Then do not let every damn thing surprise you like that, idiot.
Matoba, how would you find her?
We can assume the vampire does not know anything about Earth society.
She cannot do anything fancy to escape.
A K-9 unit would be the way to go.
The police dogs are already out there.
We have got one right here.
So she killed the guy while he was driving, and the truck crashed?
It is possible she did not attack the witnesses
because she deliberately wanted them alive.
She got out of the truck and looked at us, but then she ran that way.
It felt like she was wearing a black evening dress, but...
But it had, like, a haze around it, and kept shimmering...
One of the basic illusion spells.
It can also serve as clothing.
Which means she is got enough of her power back to use magic.
Can you use this Va... Vau...
You cannot use it when you are wearing clothes.
And it disappears immediately if you lose concentration.
No, I could tell you were by your face!
I know you are doing it!
What gives a person of lowly birth like you
-the right to look at me naked?
-the right to look at me naked?
We need to deal with the vampire.
I think she is in there.
That is the opposite of the way the witnesses said she went.
But from that building, you can overlook this area.
So she left the body for us to find in order to see how the cops would react.
Now that she is filled her belly,
what she wants most of all is information about this city.
She probably thinks she can escape from most people who would try to surround her...
I could tell from your voice.
Anyway, we are off to the mall.
I want as many men down here as you can give me.
But make sure nobody's alone for an instant.
And if you find her, do not try to catch her.
I can smell the vampire's latena.
Nothing on the security system, it looks like.
She did not trip the lasers.
Can she see lasers, you think?
If you find something, call me.
I cannot tell what direction, though.
No, you are in the way!
Why do not you give him a kiss, Tony?
We lost touch with you, so we came to save you!
And we saw you floating in the fountain...
I will get her for this.
I am amazed you are still alive.
I am amazed you are still alive.
Why have you not killed me?
So this is another world, is not it?
So the greater gate spoken of in the Book of Niba manifested?
That is what a beast does!
You do not seem to understand what hunger is.
It seems we have been interrupted.
How many of you should I eat?
She is just like a bear!
This is not just some other world.
You will find a grate up ahead.
Why the hell cannot we find her?
We have searched every inch of this damn mall!
So maybe she is not in the mall.
There is a subway 500 meters to the south.
And it is connected to the mall's ventilation system.
It is faster to go around to the East Plaza Station
and ambush her than try to go after her.
I will send you the location.
Damn it, I have been running all the time lately!
It is going to make me a healthy man.
You will not have to ride in those awful cars.
I do not know if that is good luck or bad.
I want to capture that vampire alive if possible.
You saw how strong she is!
We cannot hold back on her!
That is why I said if possible.
Did talking to her make you sympathetic?
You take pity on her for having to run around in a town she is never seen before?
She is killed two people already.
There is just something I want to ask her!
An honor to meet you, descendant of the old blood.
I apologize for being so forward.
What do you hope to gain by saving me?
Tell me what it is you desire.
I thought you might know something about such an ancient book...
Were you the one who had me brought here?
I wish merely to help you.
But with your current strength, you will be hard-pressed to escape.
They take their jobs very seriously.
I will have this man guide you.
I am disappointed, bearer of the old blood.
I died long ago in an ancient war.
This is just a brief dream before the end.
Do you want to die here with me?
No man has ever survived three battles with me.
Perhaps you were the warrior spoken of in the prophecy.
She was smashed to pieces, so...
I have not heard any thank-yous from the man
who should have been smashed to pieces, too.
I did not ask for your help.
Now let us call for backup.
Next time I am not saving you!
Anyway, we need to start on those reports...
People who get to rest in a coffin when the sun comes up sure have it easy...
Next Time Next time on COP CRAFT.
